#

Spicy Chicken Tacos with Avocado Salsa

$15.99
600 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-Free

Tags:

QuickPopularAmericanMexican

Description

Zesty and flavorful chicken tacos topped with fresh avocado salsa for a quick meal that packs a punch!

Ingredients

  • Boneless, skinless chicken thighs: 1 lb
  • Taco seasoning: 2 tbsp
  • Corn tortillas: 8
  • Avocado: 1, diced
  • Red onion: 1/2, diced
  • Cilantro: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • Lime: 1, juiced
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
